                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "EmyHV",
                      "name": "articleDeck",
                      "fill": "$text-secondary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "从输入、整理到输出，建立一套长期可复用的创作工作流，让写作从灵感依赖转向系统驱动。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.5,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "mav5x",
                      "name": "writingPaper",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "height": "fill_container",
                      "fill": "$bg-elevated",
                      "cornerRadius": 18,
                      "stroke": {
                        "thickness": 1,
                        "fill": "$line-subtle"
                      },
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 14,
                      "padding": [
                        24,
                        28
                      ],
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "UgDpZ",
                          "name": "para1",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "稳定的写作系统，不是为了让每一篇文章都更快完成，而是为了减少每次重新开始时的心理摩擦。真正有帮助的系统，会把捕捉、整理、扩写、润色这些动作放进一条平静而重复的路径里。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.65,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "RCtG4",
                          "name": "quoteBox",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "fill": "$surface-tint",
                          "cornerRadius": 14,
                          "layout": "vertical",
                          "gap": 6,
                          "padding": [
                            14,
                            16
                          ],
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "I3FVj",
                              "name": "quoteLabel",
                              "fill": "$text-tertiary",
                              "content": "Key Idea",
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 12,
                              "fontWeight": "600"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "M0sixU",
                              "name": "quoteText",
                              "fill": "$text-primary",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "好工作流不是更炫，而是更少让人犹豫。",
                              "lineHeight": 1.4,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 18,
                              "fontWeight": "500"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "K39qIX",
                          "name": "para2",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "当素材积累足够有序，写作者面对的就不再是空白页，而是一个已经有结构、有线索、有语气的半成品空间。此时编辑器的任务不是制造刺激，而是尽量安静，让判断与表达成为主角。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.65,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "i8Zicn",
                          "name": "subhead",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "content": "一、把草稿视为可持续演化的对象",
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 22,
                          "fontWeight": "600"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "CHLgz",
                          "name": "para3",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "将标题、摘要、标签与发布信息放进右侧轻量 inspector，可以显著减轻正文区的管理负担。中央区域只保留写作必要内容，既保留上下文，也避免创作时被运营信息打断。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.65,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "rectangle",
                          "id": "JQw95",
                          "name": "sectionRule",
                          "fill": "$line-subtle",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "height": 1
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "Ypb5d",
                          "name": "sectionIntro",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "content": "二、让编辑器只承担写作本身",
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 22,
                          "fontWeight": "600"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "J2Qy7",
                          "name": "sectionPara",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "当工具栏、状态、元信息都被放在稳定而次要的位置，作者就能在正文中获得接近纸稿编辑的连续性。界面不需要不断提醒 AI 的存在，它只要在需要的时候出现即可。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.65,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
